		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I was looking around a little more. LCDs deal with polarized light, so the variable you have is the orientation of the light. I searched for color polarizers and found this:
<br />
<br /><a href="http://www.patentstorm.us/patents/6498633/fulltext.html" class="postlink">http://www.patentstorm.us/patents/6498633/fulltext.html</a>
<br />
<br />It's written in Legal though, so I'll need to come back to this once I have the time to comb through it and figure out what it means, exactly.

		

		</td>
